### Vérifier le statut de complétion du profil
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fans/profile/completion
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Mettre à jour le profil (firstName)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/fans/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John"
}

### Mettre à jour le profil (lastName)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/fans/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Mettre à jour le profil (avatar)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/fans/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avatar": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### Vérifier le statut final
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/fans/profile/completion
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
